Part 3: A taste of history: TA Isolation vs Bracing
--------------------------------------------------------------

I have always considered dividing the worldwide health and fitness community into two groups. 

- "Lifting is unnecessary"  group ->  do not lift (Yogi's, Pilates folks, physiotherapists, ). They would rather stay "fit" and "healthy" than lift heavy weights. 

- "Lift or Die" aka "Meathead" group" => folks for whom lifting is the end rather than the means. Who would lift, no matter what's the result. 


There has been a long (ongoing) batter between two groups. I'd term the groups on

